			</p>
			<p>
				Treatments usually lasts 15 minutes to 1hour depending on the area to treated.  you don't have to take time off to recover-so you can resume your normal activities immediately. Laser hair removal usually requires four to six treatments and works best for people with light skin and dark hair.
